"```sql\nSELECT r.text\nFROM rulings r\nJOIN cards c ON r.uuid = c.uuid\nJOIN set_translations st ON c.setCode = st.setCode\nWHERE st.translation = 'Coldsnap' AND st.language = 'Italian';\n```\nThis SQL query selects the Italian text ruling of all the cards in the set \"Coldsnap\" by joining the `rulings`, `cards`, and `set_translations` tables based on the foreign key relationships and filtering by the specified set name and language."